
The database as a service recipe requires you to take a manual step
after deploying the OpenStack services and before you proceed to build
a disk image.

Please attach to the utility container and run the following commands:

$ . /root/openrc
$ neutron subnet-update --no-gateway trove_infra_subnet

To attach to the utility container, login to a controller node and
run the following command:

$ sudo lxc-attach -n $(sudo lxc-ls --filter=utility)
